---
title: Olive Stuffed Meatballs with Roasted Veggies
description: Tonight's tender shawarma-spiced meatballs come with a surprising twist! Their signature flavour boost comes from the addition of briny olives.  Roasted spiced peppers, carrots and onion petals round out this carb smart meal, with a drizzle of creamy hummus as the perfect zippy finish!

